#Entangle: Lowers a targets dexterity greatly.
#
#
if isInBattle caster
	livingthing target enemy caster
	chat caster "You conjure vines from the ground to hinder your foes agility."
	addconditionwithduration target "entangled" caster inte
	endscript
end
chat caster "You must be in battle to use this spell."
endscript
